  $ mkdir repo.git
  $ cd repo.git
  $ git --bare init --shared
  $ touch git-daemon-export-ok
  $ git --bare fetch /git/git_repo_with_working master:master

Now only developers with ssh access in the 'git' group (if you set it up that way) can pull / push / clone the repo.</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
